        },
        {
          "character": "可笑那汉皇帝龙身鼠胆、我父王人忠正性情太软、可笑他秉忠心不忘炎汉、虽然是众文武保孤登殿、黄须儿平日里能征惯战、面上喜心中忧长吁短叹、陈矫",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "魏王已死，天下震动，若不早立嗣王，则兄弟相争，国家危矣。何必等那木偶\n皇帝的诏？文武谁敢不服，请看此袍！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（陈矫割袍。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王朗",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "办大事不可草率，何妨请卞皇后下一道懿旨，先立世子为王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "贾诩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "名不正则言不顺，言不顺则事不成。诸君不必着急，先王必有安排。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（华歆上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "华歆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见主公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹丕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "华歆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先王已死，臣恐弟兄争位，学当年袁尚、袁谭之故事。因此威逼汉帝，写下诏\n书。特来献上。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹丕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "卿真社稷之臣也。封为相国。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华歆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢主龙恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹丕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "只怕我家兄弟们心怀不服。"
        },
        {
          "character": "华歆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先王已死，他等不来奔丧，就该问罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹丕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "言之有理，殿前指挥进见。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（指挥上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "指挥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参加殿下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹丕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "平身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "指挥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有何差遣？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹丕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤命你去到曹植、曹熊、曹彰那里，问他个不奔丧之罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "指挥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（指挥下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "华歆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣又有本启奏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹丕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "华歆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "临淄侯曹植，天下奇才，必不遵命。指挥此去，难以成功。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹丕",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "许褚过来，孤命你带定尚方宝剑，去到临淄，抓来我弟，其余之人，杀死无论。"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "领旨。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（许褚下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "华歆",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "主公尚有手足之情乎？"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹丕",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "虽然兄弟恩情厚，占我权利变仇雠。不夺王位便罢手，免得同室操戈矛。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
