    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "丁仪",
        "丁廙",
        "你好比管仲你比晏婴",
        "先王死后孝未尽",
        "指挥",
        "曹丕",
        "曹植"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四人役、丁仪、丁廙、曹植同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹植",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "盖世聪明有学问，\n眼空四海目无人。\n富贵荣华一满门。\n助纣为虐是华歆。\n家不安来国不宁。\n作两首新诗散一散心。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、指挥同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "指挥",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "人行千里路，马过万重山。"
        },
        {
          "character": "指挥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见殿下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹植",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将军少礼。到此何事？"
        },
        {
          "character": "指挥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今奉魏王之命，因殿下不奔丧，特来问罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丁仪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谁是魏王？"
        },
        {
          "character": "指挥",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "世子曹丕，诏封魏王，难道你不知道么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "丁仪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可恼哇，可恼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "丁仪",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听一言来心头恨，\n大骂曹丕不是人。\n何忍自残骨肉亲。"
        },
        {
          "character": "丁仪",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "匹夫！你可知当日先王欲立我主为世子，被谗臣所阻，才立曹丕。今先王孝服\n未满，就来问罪于骨肉，你们于心何忍？"
        },
        {
          "character": "先王死后孝未尽、丁廙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我主出口成章，比曹丕胜强十倍，反不立他为王。你等文武大臣，一味徇私，\n不识人才，令人可恨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹植",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "着着着！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹植",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我兄曹丕豺狼性，\n无端问罪骨肉亲。\n快快将他赶出门。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、指挥同下，四人役同随下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "丁仪、丁廙",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打得好！打得好！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹丕",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "叫人来酒宴安排定，"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹丕",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你我饮酒把诗吟。"
        },
        {
          "character": "你好比管仲你比晏婴、丁仪",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你好比孔圣人又复生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹植",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "自古才子多薄命，"
        },
        {
          "character": "丁廙",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "可笑曹丕是庸人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹植",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "你可知庸人有福份？"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丁廙 （同二黄原板） 运败时衰他祸临身。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹植",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我三人饮酒多高兴，\n不觉席前醉沉沉。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖急急风〗。四龙套、许褚同上，杀丁仪、丁廙，拉曹植同下。）"
        }
      ],
